d in our simulations. However, we\nfind that the same gastrophysics affects the tSZ power spectrum at ~ 40% level,\nso it is robust to infer the gastrophysics from the reconstructed redshift\nresolved contribution.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 31 Mar 2009 14:29:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 8 Apr 2010 10:08:00 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 24 Jan 2011 07:49:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-03-17"}
